'''伯尔尼大教堂'''（德语：''Berner Münster''）是一座[[哥特式|哥特式]]大教堂，位于[[瑞士|瑞士]]首都[[伯尔尼|伯尔尼]]市中心南部，北临[[座堂街|座堂街]]，西面的正立面主宰着座堂广场。教堂用砂岩砌筑，长84.2米，宽33.68米<ref name="Mojon 59">{{cite book|author=Mojon, Luc|title=Band 4: Das Berner Münster|publisher=Gesellschaft für Schweizerische Kunstgeschichte|location=Basel|year=1960|pages=59|url=http://digibiblio.unibe.ch/digibern/Chopin/Engine/Systematik/viewer.asp?KatalogID=1&ImgNum=1544|access-date=2012-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707004636/http://digibiblio.unibe.ch/digibern/Chopin/Engine/Systematik/viewer.asp?KatalogID=1&ImgNum=1544|archive-date=2011-07-07|dead-url=yes}}{{de_icon}}</ref>。始建于1421年。其钟楼高达100.6米，直到1893年才完成。它是瑞士最高的教堂，被列为[[瑞士国家和区域重要文化财产名录|国家文化财产]]<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.bevoelkerungsschutz.admin.ch/internet/bs/de/home/themen/kgs/kgs_inventar.parsys.00011.downloadList.6694.DownloadFile.tmp/abe.pdf|title= Swiss Inventory of Cultural Property of National and Regional Significance|accessdate= 2009-02-06|date= 27 November 2008}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

16世纪宗教改革后，该堂属于新教归正会，1528年清除了圣像，停止弥撒，改行新教礼拜。<ref>{{cite book |title= Famous reformers of the Reformed and Presbyterian churches |last= Good|first= James Isaac |authorlink= |coauthors= Reformed Church in the United States. Board of Home Missions, Reformed Church in the United States. Board of Foreign Missions|year= 1916|publisher= The Heidelberg press |location= |isbn= |page= |pages= 41–44 |url= http://books.google.com/books?pg=PA41&dq=Cathedral%20of%20Bern&ei=ayIGTeajHMKclgeW9OSoCg&ct=result&id=fpkSAAAAYAAJ|accessdate= 13 December 2010}}</ref>

大门上方为[[最后审判|最后审判]]雕塑，为改教后唯一保留的雕塑。钟楼向公众开放。有344级台阶通往上下两个观景台<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.berninfo.com/en/navpage-SightsBET-AttractionsBET-32346.html |title=City of Bern Tourism Site |accessdate=2012-01-06 |archive-date=2006-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061105225002/http://www.berninfo.com/en/navpage-SightsBET-AttractionsBET-32346.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

